      "id": "7753430d-59bb-40c4-a358-10006e2b127c",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(K)$ inversible et $B = A^{-1}$, $C = A^2$.\nExprimer les polynômes caractéristiques $\\chi_B$ et $\\chi_C$ en fonction de $\\chi_A$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(K)\\)</span> inversible et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(B = A^{-1}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(C = A^2\\)</span>. Exprimer les polynômes caractéristiques <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_B\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_C\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4d913048-be64-446c-8a92-bd9985d95b6f",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\chi_B(X) = \\frac{(-X)^n}{\\det(A)}\\chi_A(1/X)$,\\quad$\\chi_C(X^2) = \\chi_A(X)\\chi_A(-X)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_B(X) = \\frac{(-X)^n}{\\det(A)}\\chi_A(1/X)\\)</span>,<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_C(X^2) = \\chi_A(X)\\chi_A(-X)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
